{"tid":434871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆：相信市民不會騙取補貼","createTime":"2017-10-13T16:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T17:33:05.000Z","uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"803e3158a28fd379f6b903fd7f1e5fc167c1bc2a","tid":434871,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局長陳帆今日出席商台節目指，會考慮在無審查交通津貼計劃中，跟進涵蓋村巴和紅色小巴，亦指以現金購買渡輪月票或日票都會納入計劃中。陳帆又強調計劃的操作簡單， 系統以最低成本運作，市民不用申請和核實，可讓全部市民受惠。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆表示，會考慮跟進涵蓋村巴和紅色小巴。有市民反映，計劃應將以現金購買渡輪月票或日票都納入計劃中，陳帆指，希望有關費用都會計算在補貼計劃中，正研究在技術上如何解決問題，將補貼回饋至市民的八達通卡內。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人指計劃令走水貨、速遞人員得益，陳帆強調計劃的操作簡單易明，系統以最低成本運作，市民不用申請和核實，可讓所有市民受惠。陳帆說，現時本港使用的八達通卡有1000萬張，每個月花2000元以上交通費的市民，估計是數以千位計，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他相信市民不會騙取補貼。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a20c4975277fe3e7d8c3ee81ff6d23ea298e69","tid":434871,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"source <a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171013/s00001/1507859763485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171013%2Fs00001%2F1507859763485&d=eVjyXSMXA2%2B01%2BlJnZyYI3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=df59764d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171013%2Fs00001%2F1507859763485&h=9bc08007\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171013/s00001/1507859763485</a>"},{"pid":"ef2403ad31780cf8c4b130f98e79ba34d72b0dd4","tid":434871,"uid":127611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"冇事既,出黎行我地講個信字"},{"pid":"edda5a3751ec2c361838ab369fd6f930435dcc6e","tid":434871,"uid":42734,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"因為呃果啲唔係香港市民"},{"pid":"0b9f55be2df9b8352ce16a8fe8c66d3deb7341f2","tid":434871,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為呃果啲唔係香港市民</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d157c0a5e6a1b8d54f0f40af8a785c11d1c1182c","tid":434871,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"又唔係呃佢錢，陳帆林鄭梗無所謂<br />\n用納稅人錢收買人心"},{"pid":"a341b8e0df5b357a6dd2c72fac150fb22667d1ad","tid":434871,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"係用盡唔係呃<br />\n<br />\n又要走多兩轉了"}]}